title: Baseline Bits 02: AWS Business Support on Production AWS Accounts
description:
Learn more about the baseline! Visit the APN Technical Baseline Review page: https://amzn.to/2Y7ImfS
This episode covers the AWS Support requirement of the Technical Baseline Review (‘baseline’) and the benefits AWS Business Support offers to AWS Partner Network (APN) Partners and customers.

The baseline requires AWS Business Support or greater to be enabled on all production AWS accounts. These include accounts that are operated as part of a managed service, accounts that are essential to the proper functioning of a SaaS or other 'as-a-service' offerings, accounts from which customer-facing collateral are distributed (e.g. sharing AMIs), and accounts that contain customer data. 

The baseline is a review of an APN Partner’s solution against a set of best practices that are most critical for partner and customer success. Passing the baseline is required to qualify APN Technology Partners for APN Advanced Tier.

For more information about AWS Business Support and it’s benefits, please visit: https://aws.amazon.com/premiumsupport/

Learn more about the baseline! Watch Baseline Bits 01: What is the Technical Baseline Review? https://youtu.be/oCkcOxx96-Y.

Partners may request a baseline review through APN Partner Central: https://aws.amazon.com/partners/apn-portal/

title: AWS Support - In Autodesk's Words
description:
Learn more about AWS Support at - https://amzn.to/2L9Kb9N.
Angelo Gouvis, Senior Manager of Cloud Infrastructure at Autodesk, shares the impact AWS Support has made on Autodesk's business. AWS Support has had a transformation effect for Autodesk, freeing the company to focus on its core business. From accelerated adoption and increased innovation, through risk mitigation and improved performance, customers are leveraging AWS Support to help enable the success of their infrastructure, applications, games, and solutions.

title: AWS Enterprise Support: Customer Obsession at Work
description:
Learn more about AWS Enterprise Support at - https://amzn.to/2M15xT8.
AWS Enterprise Support offers a combination of technology, people, and proactive programs to help customers achieve success with AWS.
